Interface DataContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public interface DataContainer
extends java.lang.Cloneable
    This to better separate concerns of property list management currently mixed in PropertyListInterface. This interface isolates the block data treatments (clone, clear, fill...)
